{"tid":1772964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁定邦稱已向監警會國際專家小組說明必須按法律辦事","createTime":"2019-12-07T05:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T06:46:18.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6292690d2586fb1db08e48dec724a48739ab07e8","tid":1772964,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:49:28.000Z","msg":"監警會主席梁定邦說，香港修例風波持續時間遠超預期，局勢十分複雜，認為監警會國際專家小組，對目前局勢了解不全面。<br />\n<br />\n梁定邦接受《深圳衛視》專訪時說，國際專家小組不太明白香港現時的情況，他已經向小組說明，以香港的法律功能來說，監警會必須按法律辦事。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述梁定邦說，監警會將努力給香港警察和公眾一個公平的說法。報道又指出，監警會撰寫首階段研究範圍報告的進度，已進入最後階段，有望在本月底前，向行政長官林鄭月娥遞交報告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦監狗會"},{"pid":"dead44117bf408222519965803017a7999d4ddad","tid":1772964,"uid":76745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"專家係客觀咁檢視黑警表現係咪合法 關了唔了解香港政治咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6670edf5d8cbc1b5224a60ea590895168059aa1a","tid":1772964,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.c